From c6d2b0fbb893d5c7dda405aa0e7bcbecf1c75f98 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Veerabadhran Gopalakrishnan <veerabadhran.gopalakrishnan@amd.com>
Date: Thu, 29 Oct 2020 19:59:46 +0530
Subject: [PATCH] amd/amdgpu: Disable VCN DPG mode for Picasso
Git-commit: c6d2b0fbb893d5c7dda405aa0e7bcbecf1c75f98
Patch-mainline: v5.10-rc3
References: git-fixes

Concurrent operation of VCN and JPEG decoder in DPG mode is
causing ring timeout due to power state.

Signed-off-by: Veerabadhran Gopalakrishnan <veerabadhran.gopalakrishnan@amd.com>
Reviewed-by: Leo Liu <leo.liu@amd.com>
Signed-off-by: Alex Deucher <alexander.deucher@amd.com>
Acked-by: Takashi Iwai <tiwai@suse.de>

---
 drivers/gpu/drm/amd/amdgpu/soc15.c | 3 +--
 1 file changed, 1 insertion(+), 2 deletions(-)

diff --git a/drivers/gpu/drm/amd/amdgpu/soc15.c b/drivers/gpu/drm/amd/amdgpu/soc15.c
index afcccc6c0fc6..eff68fb532ce 100644
--- a/drivers/gpu/drm/amd/amdgpu/soc15.c
+++ b/drivers/gpu/drm/amd/amdgpu/soc15.c
@@ -1195,8 +1195,7 @@ static int soc15_common_early_init(void *handle)
 
 			adev->pg_flags = AMD_PG_SUPPORT_SDMA |
 				AMD_PG_SUPPORT_MMHUB |
-				AMD_PG_SUPPORT_VCN |
-				AMD_PG_SUPPORT_VCN_DPG;
+				AMD_PG_SUPPORT_VCN;
 		} else {
 			adev->cg_flags = AMD_CG_SUPPORT_GFX_MGCG |
 				AMD_CG_SUPPORT_GFX_MGLS |
-- 
